### Documentation Guidelines

1. Project Structure Documentation
- Maintain REORGANISATION.md:
  - Document all structural changes
  - Explain reorganization rationale
  - Track directory structure updates
  - Document migration steps

2. Testing Documentation
- Maintain TESTING_STRATEGY.md:
  - Document test organization
  - Explain testing approaches
  - List required test coverage
  - Provide testing examples

3. Code Documentation
- Clear function/method docstrings
- Module-level documentation
- Type hints and annotations
- Architecture documentation
- API endpoint documentation

4. Change Management
- Document all API changes
- Update documentation with code
- Version documentation with code
- Track breaking changes

5. Developer Guides
- Setup instructions
- Development environment
- Contribution guidelines
- Troubleshooting guide
- API usage examples